{"tid":1582311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Massive Attack多倫多開騷播港警打人片","createTime":"2019-09-20T04:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:18:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1ec9b245702d4c4063c12061d1abf75008ac93","tid":1582311,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190920/20771488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771488&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=c7b02e0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771488&h=3100e98d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190920/20771488</a><br />\n<br />\nMassive Attack多倫多開騷播港警打人片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190920/large/1568902170_c972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568902170_c972.jpg&h=7f8712b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMassive Attack主音Robert<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國Trip Hop班霸Massive Attack前晚於加拿大多倫多舉行演唱會，唱到壓軸歌曲《Group four》時，在台上播出香港警方於7月14日在沙田新城市廣場濫捕示威者的片段，以表達對香港人的支持。片段中，共逾10名警察在鏡頭下，仍然毆打手無寸鐵的市民，而《Group four》的歌詞正是關於政府對人民的監控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190920/large/1568902170_6ecb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568902170_6ecb.gif&h=c60c67ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMassive Attack前晚在多倫多開騷，在台上播出香港警方打人的片段。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n其實，Massive Attack一向都很關注香港的政治狀況，他們曾於2017年來港在Clockenflap演出，當時他們亦有在舞台上展示和平佔中的標誌，以及黃之鋒的頭像等支持社運。主音Robert&quot;3D&quot; Del Naja當時接受本報訪問時，就關心本港貧富懸殊與民主的問題，當時他說：「我簡直覺得十分瘋狂，尤其是這處貧富懸殊的狀況，一條橋劃分出兩個不同的世界。我覺得香港的歷史背景讓它成為一個很有趣的地方。首先，曾經作為英國殖民地對於這個地方的影響，我覺得很好奇。我覺得歷史非常重要，而因為殖民的關係，英國變成了歷史重要的部份。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：克己 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【台日合作】李心潔阿部寬壓軸重頭戲"},{"pid":"1a7585f918b67060a553e4bea1d7470707c5e5f2","tid":1582311,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=ce8a6f07\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=fb5e2261\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"e35cff374b3a70f42efa4beb3ad48566efee6413","tid":1582311,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"傳說3D係banksy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08a87fe5aa6ca3ed78958a36d1adcd4aaeb5047","tid":1582311,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n請求美國制裁香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-police\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-po