xQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ch4X7sO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fch4X7sO.jpg&h=971c9013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">花式！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kpuJnC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kpuJnC.gif&h=c1c29c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOXL09p.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOXL09p.gif&h=da33a572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P9O0kzY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9O0kzY.gif&h=f7f52476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNTfvwM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNTfvwM.jpg&h=6cb0c505&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1DfvwN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1DfvwN.jpg&h=6f8fb244&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2riOQwO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2riOQwO.jpg&h=074cd595&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCaEXbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCaEXbO.jpg&h=0736be80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shojk9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fshojk9N.jpg&h=e87f4f61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u72wcgs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu72wcgs.jpg&h=4e7ea801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdRT928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdRT928.jpg&h=fe5ef654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCfhVw9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCfhVw9.jpg&h=cc4a2b71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6BpAxa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6BpAxa.jpg&h=4f61ec87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRYWrDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRYWrDQ.jpg&h=7f1b8468&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1orOSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1orOSa.jpg&h=6f8244b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOobZYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOobZYR.jpg&h=d87249b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n@期望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n預備大型商場不合作運動：<br />\n齋睇唔買，儲多d錢；人多自然塞<br />\n連儂牆戰線不能倒！修建連儂，有你有我<br />\n<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</span><br />\n<em>每日任務：</em><br />\n1. 優先<span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心商店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>（注意安全）；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=b5ab6c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF轉美國<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.14</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a6acde41d0a11b84c50e14ab90a51229c8d5c15e","tid":1582311,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee1ec9b245702d4c4063c12061d1abf75008ac93","tid":1582311,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190920/20771488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771488&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=c7b02e0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190920%2F20771488&h=3100e98d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190920/20771488</a><br />\n<br />\nMassive Attack多倫多開騷播港警打人片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190920/large/1568902170_c972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568902170_c972.jpg&h=7f8712b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMassive Attack主音Robert<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國Trip Hop班霸Massive Attack前晚於加拿大多倫多舉行演唱會，唱到壓軸歌曲《Group four》時，在台上播出香港警方於7月14日在沙田新城市廣場濫捕示威者的片段，以表達對香港人的支持。片段中，共逾10名警察在鏡頭下，仍然毆打手無寸鐵的市民，而《Group four》的歌詞正是關於政府對人民的監控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190920/large/1568902170_6ecb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568902170_6ecb.gif&h=c60c67ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMassive Attack前晚在多倫多開騷，在台上播出香港警方打人的片段。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n其實，Massive Attack一向都很關注香港的政治狀況，他們曾於2017年來港在Clockenflap演出，當時他們亦有在舞台上展示和平佔中的標誌，以及黃之鋒的頭像等支持社運。主音Robert&quot;3D&quot; Del Naja當時接受本報訪問時，就關心本港貧富懸殊與民主的問題，當時他說：「我簡直覺得十分瘋狂，尤其是這處貧富懸殊的狀況，一條橋劃分出兩個不同的世界。我覺得香港的歷史背景讓它成為一個很有趣的地方。首先，曾經作為英國殖民地對於這個地方的影響，我覺得很好奇。我覺得歷史非常重要，而因為殖民的關係，英國變成了歷史重要的部份。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：克己 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【台日合作】李心潔阿部寬壓軸重頭戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"9455050cf9821a4b3bc8756afc493a262715fd39","tid":1582311,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bae829bf02140c07660a5293bf1f94f451895b6","tid":1582311,"uid":195574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed13d2ebf59899ff83f89f9b44cdab04c008231","tid":1582311,"uid":196141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20